# Rust build artifacts
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Note: Cargo.lock IS committed. This crate produces a binary (`simctl`), and the
# convention for applications is to commit the lockfile for reproducible builds.
# (The core is dependency-free, so the lockfile is trivial — but kept for habit.)

